---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Car Rental Madinat Jumeirah 2026 — From AED 35/day"
  description="Compare car rentals near Madinat Jumeirah. Art Dubai venue. Economy from AED 35/day with hotel delivery. Book early for April 17–19."
>
<div class="bg-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-blue-300 mb-2">📍 Madinat Jumeirah</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Car Rental Madinat Jumeirah — From AED 35/day</h1>
  <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare car rental companies near Madinat Jumeirah — home of Art Dubai. Hotel delivery included. Book early for April events.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=madinat-jumeirah" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Get Madinat Jumeirah Car Rental Quotes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-4 mb-10">
    <iframe src="https://www.discovercars.com/engine/rent-a-car/iframe?a_aid=YOUR_AFFILIATE_ID&location=Madinat+Jumeirah+Dubai&lang=en&curr=AED" width="100%" height="420" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" title="Madinat Jumeirah Car Rental — Compare Prices"></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Car Rental at Madinat Jumeirah</h2>
    <p>Madinat Jumeirah is a luxury resort complex and the permanent home of Art Dubai, the Middle East's largest art fair held annually in April (April 17–19 in 2026). During Art Dubai week, car rental demand in the area spikes significantly.</p>
    <p>The Madinat area includes the Al Qasr, Mina A'Salam, and Jumeirah Beach hotels, plus the Souk Madinat shopping area. Car rental operators deliver to all hotels in the complex, with economy cars from AED 35/day.</p>
    <p>Madinat Jumeirah is located between Dubai Marina and Downtown Dubai on Jumeirah Beach Road. A rental car gives easy access to both areas plus the wider Dubai attractions. Valet parking is available at all Madinat venues.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/car-rentals" class="text-brand font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all car rental areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
